# Swegue API

Swegue is a simple API allowing consumers to view information on Marvel Comics.
Our source can be found here: https://github.com/nickroberts404/cs373-idb

## Comics Collection [/comics]

### List All Comics [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Schema
        
            {
                "type": "object",
                "required": true,
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "properties": {
                    "comics": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "required": true,                            "description": "List of all Comics"
                    }
                }
            }
    
