## Query Comics [/comics/{comic_id}]

+ Parameters
    + comic_id (number) - Integer identifier of the comic


### Comic Details [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Schema
        
            {
                "type": "object",
                "required": true,
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "properties": {
                    "thumbnail": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "URL of a thumbnail image for this comic"
                    },
                    "id": {
                        "type": "number",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "Comic id"
                    },
                    "title": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "Comic Title"
                    },
                    "issue_number": {
                        "type": "number",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "Issue Number"
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "Description of the Comic"
                    },
                    "page_count": {
                        "type": "number",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "Comic Page Count"
                    },
                    "characters": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "List of characters in the comic"
                    },
                    "creators": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "required": true,
                        "description": "List of creators of the comic"
                    }
                }
            }
        
